<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
      <meta charset="utf-8">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-1q8mTJOASx8j1Au+a5WDVnPi2lkFfwwEAa8hDDdjZlpLegxhjVME1fgjWPGmkzs7" crossorigin="anonymous">
      <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
      <title>Image Search Abstraction Layer</title>
    </head>
    <body>
      <main>
        <h1>Image Search Abstraction Layer</h1>
        <article>
          <p>Use the endpoint <code>results/?term=**Your Query** </code> to get metadata for the top image search results</p>
          <p>You can paginate the results by adding a query to the endpoint like <code>results/term?=puppies&offset=2</code></p>
          <p>To get a json object of the most recent search strings, use <code>/recent?json=true</code></p>
        </article>
        <form method="get" action="/results">
          <input type="text" name="term" class="search-bar">
          <input type="submit" value="Search" class="btn">
        </form>
        {{#if image}}
          {{>results}} 
        {{/if}}
        {{#if terms}}
          {{>searchTerms}}
        {{/if}}       
      <main>    
    <body>    
</html>